* Matt Miller – bass, backing vocals 

;Current touring musicians
* Neil Hennessy – drums 

;Former members
* Tony Hajjar – drums 
* Paul Hinojos – guitar, backing vocals 
* Erick Sanger – bass 
* Gabriel Gonzalez – guitar, keyboards 
* Keeley Davis – guitar, backing vocals 
* Cully Symington – drums 

